'''Yuka Laka's Droid Materials''' was a building in the settlement of [[Anchorhead/Legends|Anchorhead]] on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Tatooine/Legends|Tatooine]] around the time of the [[Jedi Civil War]]. It was operated by an [[Ithorian/Legends|Ithorian]] named [[Yuka Laka]]. The shop primarily sold repair and upgrade parts for [[Droid/Legends|droids]], though it also sold actual droids as well as parts. In [[3956 BBY]] [[Revan/Legends|Revan]] purchased the [[Assassin droid/Legends|assassin droid]] [[HK-47]] from this store. At the time, Yuka Laka was also working on a [[Cleaning droid/Legends|utility droid]] and a [[Autoturret/Legends|turret]]. There was an inoperative [[Protocol droid/Legends|protocol droid]] in one corner of the shop.

